Demo7-Restore and delete using kustomization tool
=====
Deploy
oc apply -k config7/
SHOW THE OUTPUT
SHOW HOW TO DELETE
oc delete -k config7/
AGAIN DEPLOY
oc apply -k config7/
COMPARE AND SHOW OUTPUT
oc diff -k config7/
EDIT REPLICA VALUE
oc edit deployment 
COMPARE AND SHOW OUTPUT
oc diff -k config7/
oc get pod
SHOW THE OUTPUT
RESTORE
oc apply -k config7/
oc get pod
oc diff -k config7/
